text:
Subject: Your Account Needs Update | {online service provider name}
Dear Valued Customer,
We have received a notification that there are some inaccurate and incorrect information in your account details. Therefore, we kindly ask you to update it as soon as possible so that our system will be able to process further transactions for your convenience and safety of your personal data.

Here are the updated details: 
- Old Account Username: {original username} 
- New Account Username: {updated username} 
- Email Address: {updated email address} 

Once you have successfully made the updates, kindly proceed by clicking on the link provided below to access your account and update the necessary information:
Link here...
Thank you for your cooperation.
Sincerely,
{online service provider name}
PS: Please make sure that all the information provided are correct and accurate so as to avoid any unauthorized activity on your account. We assure you of utmost confidentiality regarding your personal data.
